// [automatic scan] Issues: 1  | Surplus trailing whitespace at line 1
@32603 = ~If you think of any questions in your travels, be sure to write them down! Return to me if you wish to continue your lessons.~

// [automatic scan] Issues: 1  | Surplus trailing whitespace at line 1
